{
  "id": "adv_main_03_12_03",
  "title": "BIG4編1章58話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyodorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.9933333278
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "――という感じで考えてみたんだけど……どうかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’ve been thinking about it like that…what do you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.7666667621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "『照らす』……かぁ\nうん、とってもいいと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Light”…huh?\nYeah‚ I think it’s really good‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.9999999921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "私達が今まで考えていたことも\nすっきり言語化されたような感じがしますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It feels like what we’ve been thinking about\nhas been clearly put into words‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.0666666587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね。今思うと、琴乃ちゃんが脱退するまで\n月ストの中心はずっと琴乃ちゃんだったよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right‚ Now that I think about it‚\nKotono-chan was always at the center of Moon Tempest until she left‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.0999999921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "少々悔しいですが……琴乃は、いつもまっすぐに\n私達の進む道を照らしてくれていましたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a little frustrating‚ but…Kotono was always straightforwardly\nlighting the way forward for us‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9433341265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ。だから私達も、勇気を持って\n迷いなく進むことが出来たんだと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I think that’s why we were able to move forward\nwith courage and without hesitation‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.5999999921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんがいなくなっちゃった時は\n凄く寂しかったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When Kotono-chan wasn’t here…\n…I was really lonely…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.2999999921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "でもね、そんな状況だったから\n芽衣達は、自分達で道を照らそうって思えたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you know‚ because we were in that situation…\n…we thought we had to light the way ourselves‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.3333333254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "心もとない薄明かりを頼りに、歯を食いしばって\n進み続けて……ようやく分かったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Relying on that faint glimmer of light‚ we gritted our teeth\nand kept moving forward…and finally understood‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.6333333254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_moon-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 69.80272309
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "「ああ、琴乃ちゃんだけじゃないんだ」って\n私達も道を照らし出す月に……光になれるんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Ah‚ it’s not just Kotono-chan‚”\nThat we can also become the moon that illuminates the path…we can become light‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.3999999921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "五人が、月に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The five of us…as the moon…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.9847415608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "私達はもう、琴乃ちゃんに頼りっきりにはならない\n今なら、五人で支え合っていけると思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We won’t rely on you so much anymore‚ Kotono-chan‚\nI believe we can support each other now‚ as five‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.0999979575,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "今の私達なら……新生月ストならば\n一人一人が確かな役割を持てるのではなくて？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With the current us…with the new Moon Tempest…\n…wouldn’t each and every one of us be able to have a definite role?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.6981189649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "一人一人が、誰かにとっての月で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Each and every one of us‚ is a moon for someone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.9710445087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "一人一人が、誰かにとっての嵐になる……\nといったところでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And every one of us‚ becomes a storm for someone…\n…I suppose‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.6333312909,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "私達一人一人が、誰かを照らす月になる\nそして……一人一人が、誰かの迷いを払う嵐になる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Each and every one of us becomes a moon that illuminates someone‚\nand…every one of us becomes a storm that sweeps away someone’s hesitation‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.2999999921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "それが、私達の……月ストにとっての――\nアイドルとして成し遂げたいこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That is our…Moon Tempest’s――\n…what we want to achieve as idols‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.0666625898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.4638753575
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.4638753575
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 132.7138753575
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "月ストの……五人の答えが見つかったんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moon Tempest…you five have found your answer‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.5138753575,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.7704513711
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "私達は……もう迷いません\n今度こそ、どりきゅんに挑戦させて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We…won’t hesitate anymore‚\nPlease let us challenge DoriKyun this time‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.1666605552,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そう……だな。そうしたいのはやまやまなんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I…see‚ I’d love to‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.7057805222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.1832410973
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんですの？　やけに歯切れが悪いですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s wrong? You sound awfully hesitant‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.1832410973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.1852821511
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "みんなが答えを探している間、俺もどりきゅんと\n再戦出来ないか、先方に掛け合っていたんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "While you all were searching for your answer‚\nI was trying to arrange a rematch with DoriKyun‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.4804376763,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "状況が思わしくないんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is the situation not looking good?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.4364615601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.7599764508
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そう……なんだ。申し訳ない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s…right‚ I’m sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.7599764508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.7412011784
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "今まで二戦ともあっさり決まったのに……\nどうしてなんだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The last two battles were decided so easily…\n…why is this happening?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.3666605552,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 176.3706569355
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 176.3706569355
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_03-ktn006.m4a",
